* Carnage snarled as she came to a rise, they had passed the old Maximal 
base's location mega-cycles ago and were now very close to the signatures 
that she had first detected. She didn't like the way that Cyber Claw spoke 
to her but there wasn't much that she could do about it, she just had to put 
up with the banter until Megatron was dead...then she wouldn't have to put 
up with this clone any longer!
She snapped her head around and came snout to snout with Cyber Claw, she 
snarled...*

" Mind I remind you that it was YOU who asked to come with US. So settle 
down and hold your horses, alright. We'll get where ever we're going when we 
get there and not before!"

* She looked ahead again and began to make her way towards the signatures 
that she was still detecting, she wasn't truly angry but she had enough to 
think about without a loud mouth clone bitching at her!*

" Now, come on."

*Carnage sighed and looked around, they were near the signatures but there 
was nothing there. Just...the sea.
She came to the edge of the beach and opened her com-link to a Maximal's 
only frequency...*

" This is to any Maximals in the area, we request permission to make 
contact. Our coordinates are 315.668. Please respond."

* She listened to the static of her open channel, the signatures were there 
but she just couldn't seem to find them with her optics. Her system's showed 
that they were only a few hundred clicks ahead of them but there was nothing 
there...but blue sea.*

(She is in front of the island on the mainland.)
